{"tid":1538501,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緊急呼籲巴打絲打盡快推上 Twitter 民權法一定要通過","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T00:32:25.000Z","uid":193220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cd49bdc7adbbeffbf2ff82e861e79b363a2c8c63","tid":1538501,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:10:59.000Z","msg":"緊急呼籲巴打絲打盡快推上 Twitter<br />\n民權法一定要通過<br />\n<br />\n唔可以比林鄭黑狗 奸計得逞"},{"pid":"e4077287fe53bb9323a049680ba89cb5afefaf42","tid":1538501,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0a7bb4cd13bfef60fe71d37fe357faccc2cf4cc","tid":1538501,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kybLqX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkybLqX5.jpg&h=ae2d5f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n入嚟幫手推<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"d326a7e5bc322c13ace1f65ddf330c635ece3192","tid":1538501,"uid":2036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd49bdc7adbbeffbf2ff82e861e79b363a2c8c63","tid":1538501,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:10:59.000Z","msg":"緊急呼籲巴打絲打盡快推上 Twitter<br />\n民權法一定要通過<br />\n<br />\n唔可以比林鄭黑狗 奸計得逞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:14:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">因為美國先會撤 你估唔罰班狗官會點</span><br />\n<br />\n國歌 國教 大嶼 慢慢玩<br />\n<br />\n千幾個拉左 爆眼 裸搜 濫捕<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">去左台灣流亡緊既7.1 手足仲係無辨法返黎</span><br />\n國泰,教協清算..<br />\n一隻狗都無事 點可以收手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一定要堅持到人權法通過</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. Please pass Hong Kong Human Right and Democracy Act<br />\n2. Grant a true autonomy for HK, or impose sanctions on HK by cancelling United States&ndash;Hong Kong Policy Act<br />\n3. Impose sanction on officials of HK and China, whom proposed to amend extradition bill<br />\n4. Impose sanction on all Hong Kong policemen, who exercise excessive force against protestors"},{"pid":"2afa1776dd9d6d9cb39be517ddf828a56848190f","tid":1538501,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:21:11.000Z","msg":"係咁推啦"},{"pid":"d9356268e371351f2b68e09a110480d001182fef","tid":1538501,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e37e34ff8d78053047880a14cadbf2f7742b273","tid":1538501,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"64ad747e4cf759c4b216cc4879393f61acc8c266","tid":1538501,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3732d8491d9cd578f22ec38e927e1abeeb456828","tid":1538501,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n<br />\n分別在於:<br />\n3隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n8人離世<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"56ac6fcd8ebb8c881e7ae622ae9a200841ef576a","tid":1538501,"uid":303463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:01:33.000Z","msg":"［今晚9點twitter戰線］推五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539091</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9bd47602ecc527267841ebd47fa1afe043616909","tid":1538501,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998f52181ae6f0f26dcb2404e1c7e4b41ae86e89","tid":1538501,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:44:48.000Z","msg":"🇺🇸"},{"pid":"807b814289313474476c913f69fadf6f7cd3da69","tid":1538501,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a78d17987aa6d3364a3a280d39dc322cf6af2a52","tid":1538501,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm